The Followers
by Jean-SÃ©bastien Fauteux

Requirement to build:

-SFML 2.x (Originally built with 2.0 RC)
-Pugixml 1.4 (The library given comes built for Visual Studio 2013)

*Note: If you use SFML 2.2 and higher, you will need to manually specify additional library to link.
*Note: The library given for pugixml is built for Visual Studio 2013. You will need to built the library yourself other platform.

First Release: May 2012
